![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1601417717759-ZCXUN6XVGY37DQZBUQ8S/Burning146.jpg?format=original)

The Sorcerer Supreme has been SHOT! When the Sanctum Sanctorum is broken into and Dr. Strange is shot, it's up to the veteran magic-user to track down the culprits and retrieve one of the most sought-after items he has even been in possession of...a cure for all disease. Can the former surgeon solve the mystery and save the world from a mysterious and malicious threat? Tune in to our review of **Dr. Strange: The Oath** and find out! If you're a Dr. Strange fan, this episode is can't miss and just what the doctor ordered.

